org.eclipse.californium.core.network

Class CoapEndpoint.OutboxImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.californium.core.network.CoapEndpoint.OutboxImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Outbox
    Enclosing class:
    CoapEndpoint

    public class CoapEndpoint.OutboxImpl
extends Object
implements Outbox
    The stack of layers uses this Outbox to send messages. The OutboxImpl will then give them to the matcher, the interceptors, and finally send them over the connector.
